'''Steel Design, Fourth Edition by Segui''' is [[textbook]] published by [[Cengage Learning]] TM.

This text firmly addresses all aspects and [[physics]] of designing [[steel]] structures in the [[United States]]. The book references the Steel Construction Manual written and approved by [[American Institute of Steel Construction]]. The manual is referenced for the specifications of steel members, it introduces a structured way of learning how to design using the manual.

